Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到魔多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Mordor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意发誓效忠阿达尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you swear allegiance to Adar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没什么好怕的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no one left for us to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个 一名远古妖术师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is one. An ancient sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放了我的子民 我就告诉你那名妖术师在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set my people free, and I will tell you where he can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能消灭他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you can destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother. Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有座火山苏醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fire-mountain awoke. -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,随之产生的地动山摇 却沿着大地之骨一路蔓延过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ground-shakes it produced spread through the bones of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁了我们的矿井\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}collapsing our sun-shafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗之手已包覆卡扎督姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hand of darkness has closed around Khazad-d?m.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听不到山的声音了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't hear the mountains anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,此时此刻整个中洲正岌岌可危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At this very moment, all Middle-earth balances on the brink of the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,力量之戒是我们重返光明的最后机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Rings of Power are our last hope of restoring the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是某种邀请...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's some sort of invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来自凯勒布林博大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from Lord Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,努门诺尔岛国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Island Kingdom of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经有七颗真知晶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven Seeing Stones there once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这一颗传到我父王手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one was passed to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁愿意承担保护摄政女王的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is willing to commit themselves to our Queen-regent's protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意效力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,–我愿意效力  –我愿意效力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I will serve! - I will serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,–法拉宗  –跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n! Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么不阻止这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't he stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,–他对她很忠诚 无论对或... –错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's loyal to her. Rightly or... - Wrongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你堂姐手握权杖 但人民追随的是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your cousin may hold the scepter, but it's you the people follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,–有他们支持 你可以... –可以怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With their help you could... Could what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,发挥你的影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assert your influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,–找掩护  –女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take shelter! - The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}指环王:力量之戒\N第二季第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖回家 听到没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're going home. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,–拜托了 –它不会听你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. He won't listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它不会听我们任何人的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He won't listen to any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别害怕 四条腿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be afraid, four-legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会吃了你 暂时不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ain't gonna eat ya... yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,逮到你啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, got ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别想跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,–跑掉了 快追啊  –算了 让它去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No! It's getting away! After it! - No! Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前面是暗黑森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That there's the Black Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没东西能活着出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin' comes outta there alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,贝雷克 走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berek, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,努门诺尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,国王始终保护着忠贞派 我会想念他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As king he always protected The Faithful. I shall miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你侃侃而谈死去的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak so freely of dead kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,却不愿提及你儿子的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}yet you refuse to utter your own son's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不需自责 该责怪的另有其人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You blame yourself but you needn't. True blame belongs to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 我们岛国就要灭亡了 还有时间...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So know this, our island will fall, and there is still time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen-regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,北方的贵族来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The nobles from the North are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔札加尔大人看来是来致敬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems Lord Belzagar has come to pay his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没敬意的人是无法致敬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One cannot pay what one does not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他听信法拉宗 还是反过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does Pharaz?n have his ear or is it the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,后者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen-regent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就这样回报逝去之人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this how we repay our fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,–这只是开始... –不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It is only the beginning of our-- - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait! [panting] Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你失去了什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is it you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲的遗物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Your father's effects? - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听到你进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't hear you come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,死者的遗物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Possessions of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,将成为神圣的钥匙 能打开永远紧闭的大门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They become hallowed keys into doors that are, now, forever shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得我父亲去世的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember when my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我盯着一个杯子看 里面是他前一晚喝剩一半的酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looking at a cup, half-filled with wine he'd drunk the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,把酒倒掉感觉像是种背叛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seemed a betrayal to empty the glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但他也讨厌浪费好酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he also hated wasting good wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我喝掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I drank it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你来做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你藏在背后的东西 我就告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show me what you hide behind your back, and I will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 堂弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你该做出选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it is time for you to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的礼服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要深红色 代表努门诺尔的未来 还是白色 代表过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crimson, for Númenor's future, or white, her past?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么场合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你的加冕大典\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们哀悼死者够久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have mourned the dead long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也该关心一下生者了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is time that we attend to the concerns of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲当年选择白色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father wore white.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我只记得这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all I can recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大鹰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That, and an eagle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,用大鹰来装饰加冕大典很罕见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is rare for an eagle to grace a coronation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有只大鹰出现在加冕大典上 会被视为吉兆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should one make an appearance at yours, it would be seen as an auspicious omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就白色吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The white, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我偏爱红色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm partial to the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“如同太阳 新的君主冉冉升起”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Like the sun, rises a new monarch."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能向人民展示 你是新时代新形态的统治者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will show the people you're a new kind of ruler for a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,人民需要改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还是白色吧 比较谦逊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The white. It is humbler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,悉听尊便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟她父亲一样 永远不知变通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's the same as her father, she's never going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她身体有恙 不再适合治国了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's suffered an infirmity. She's no longer fit to rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,笑什么 这是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why laugh? It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,醉话而已 醉了还是别大声嚷嚷比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is the ale talking. It would be wise to lower its voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此 这孩子没说错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the same, the boy's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你差点就被选中代替她掌权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were nearly chosen to rule in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这片土地仍有多数人认为 你是更好的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much of this land still believes that yours was the better claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在弥瑞尔的好战之举后 多数人准备再次提出质疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And after Míriel's warmongering, many are ready to raise it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“多数人”是不足以推翻女王的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Many" is hardly enough to supplant a Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen-regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一介盲目之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A blind one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有人知道怎么把 “多数人”变成“够多人”呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if someone knew a way to turn "many" into "enough"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,既然知道 为什么不说出来呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the event that someone did, why would they not bring it forth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可能害怕后果吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They might be afraid of what could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这张桌子上没什么好怕的 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is nothing to fear at this table, my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,埃雅瑞恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}E?rien?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought that was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,维蓝迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为公会的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I thought Guilds-folk preferred
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,偏爱待在更时尚的地方呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to keep to the more fashionable part of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来旧城区干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing in the Old Quarter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来安葬国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came here to bury a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,愿维拉让他安息并守护他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Valar rest him and keep him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我能在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've liked to have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜一般士兵没有受邀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pity members of the common soldiery weren't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其考虑到那些底层民众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially given the low class of folk that were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚是在羞辱我父亲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you just insult my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在羞辱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I believe I insulted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟女王一同上战场洒热血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bled with the Queen on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼看着她冲进地狱里救人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I watched her walk into an inferno to save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,试图拯救她哥哥的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To try and save her brother's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再敢说女王的不是 身体有恙的就会是你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak ill of the Queen again, it'll be you, suffers an infirmity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我说得够清楚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I made myself plain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还是要用其他方式解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or need we settle this through other means?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天够清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plain enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来需要再来一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd say that's worth another ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,埃雅瑞恩 你刚讲到哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was it you were about to say, E?rien?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现某个东西...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,天大秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,相当危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,禁忌之物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,领主大人 准备工作就快完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The preparations are nearly complete, Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只是...我们在这里很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But... we are safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有自己的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要再次开战吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must we go to war again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说索隆已经死了 那就当他死了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me Sauron was dead. Let us leave him that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,身为父亲有责任了解世上的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are some dangers in this world about which it is a father's burden to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子有责任相信父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And a son's burden to trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me, my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,除非确定索隆彻底消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I tell you that we will never truly be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们永远不会真正安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until we've made certain Sauron is no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命 领主大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you will it, Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be off, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,戴莫德 灰色山脉山岭食人妖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damrod. Hill-troll of the Ered Mithrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,石巨人杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Killer of stone giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,龙骨掠食者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eater of Dragon bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你收到我们的讯息了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gather you received our message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,索隆在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 谢谢你们专程前来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome. Thank you for making the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里你无需隐藏你的烦恼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need not hide your troubles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无意加以利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have no intention to take advantage of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,单纯只想提供帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}simply, to, to render aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如同你们曾经帮助过我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you once did us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为你能提供什么样的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And exactly what aid do you think you could provide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,中洲 强大无比的矮人诸王各持一只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One for each of Middle-earth's most powerful Dwarf-lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你找我们来就为了交易珠宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You brought us here to barter jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这些戒指的力量 将超越矮人 人类或精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These Rings will be beyond any power yet devised
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所能生成的任何力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by Dwarf, or Man, or Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这些戒指将是力量之戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They shall be Rings of Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,足以治愈你们的山脉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Power to heal your mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如同治愈了我们的圣树\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as they have healed our Great Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔隆德...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mithril?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,秘银扭转了我们的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mithril has reversed our fortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,相信也能扭转你们的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe it can do the same for yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至整个中洲所有种族的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps, for all the peoples of Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只要稳定提供秘银就好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we provide you with a steady supply, is that the sum of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,秘银 用来打造戒指 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mithril, for Rings. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,凯勒布林博大人 这提议太慷慨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A generous offer, Lord Celebrimbor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但为何不直接找我们国王呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but why not take it to our King?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老都林国王对于接受外援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Durin the Elder has always been hesitant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一向有所犹豫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to accept outside aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们的提议由他自己人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if our proposal was brought to him instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,提出来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by one of his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我父亲已经不再交谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father and I are no longer on speaking terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都林的意思是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What Durin means--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要我们两个共处一室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd sooner convince an Orc
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如叫半兽人去晒太阳还比较快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to sit for a sun-bath, than get the two of us in a room together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕是帮不上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid, I'd be of little help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找你来是要帮助你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We summoned you here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为你父亲献上拯救王国的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bringing your father a means of saving his kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.62,0:23:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,或许正好能赢回他对你的尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might be just the way to earn back his respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至你的继承资格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps, even your inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 请问你哪位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我的疏忽 这位是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, forgive me. This is--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一个朋友 精灵的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A friend. To the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也是矮人的朋友 如此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to the Dwarves. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 埃尔隆德在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see. And where's Elrond?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,修复林顿需要他全神贯注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lindon's restoration demands his full attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证埃尔隆德传令官一心挂念着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assure you, Herald Elrond said he could think of little else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要帮助他的矮人朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than helping his Dwarven friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他提起你时很关心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He speaks of you so fondly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,妙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他从没提起过你 这位...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's never mentioned you. Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,安那塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Annatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔隆德说你是矮人族中 最有智慧的一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond said that you were the wisest of all the Dwarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的是真的 还是我们应该找其他人谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he speak true, or is there someone else we should be treating with?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,两位大人 你们的提议需要深思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Lords, you've given us much to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能给我们一点时间考虑一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might we have a wee moment to, uh, to mull it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,–我们恐怕... –当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am afraid we-- Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take whatever time you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.79,0:24:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么 是想找人吵架吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you thinking? Were you trying to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想 不管那个安那塔是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was thinking, whoever that Annatar is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.37,0:24:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟埃尔隆德一点也不熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he doesn't know Elrond from a hole in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.45,0:24:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.62,0:24:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为埃尔隆德 不可能把我说得那么好听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause Elrond would never say such nice things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点都不心动吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aren't you in the least bit relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.58,0:24:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啦 可是魔法戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but magic rings?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.87,0:24:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得听起来非常诡异吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does no part of this sound strange to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那得由你父亲来决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's for your father to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.37,0:24:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他听都没听过 是要怎么决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be hard for him to decide about a proposal he never hears.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.54,0:24:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,重点就在这吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.91,0:24:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你宁愿看着我们的山脉毁灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd sooner let our entire mountain roast and rot,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.75,0:24:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也不愿说一声对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than have to say you were sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.58,0:25:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你宁愿让全家人吃虫子 也不愿向他承认...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd sooner feed our family slugworms, than admit to him that you--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我认同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.66,0:25:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但你现在错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're wrong now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.45,0:25:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我管他什么魔法耳环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care if they're magic earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.79,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有一丝丝希望 不管听起来多么牵强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there's even a hope of a solution here, no matter how farfetched,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的国王都应该要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our King needs to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.33,0:25:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要嘛你去跟你父亲说 要嘛我去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either you bring news of this to your father, or I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.41,0:25:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在卡扎督姆有句俗话说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a saying, in Khazad-d?m,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.83,0:25:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,“滴水能穿石”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The slow drip splits the boulder."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.58,0:25:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So give them time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.87,0:25:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,时间是我们最缺乏的奢侈品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And time is a luxury we lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,万一你的至高王发现...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposing your High King were to discover...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,至高王怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the High King?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.16,0:25:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 我不该说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:26:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么 快说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Say what? Speak plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.29,0:26:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的至高王认为 矮人不配拥有这种力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your High King believes the Dwarves to be unworthy of this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.37,0:26:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 他禁止再打造任何戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, he has forbidden the forging of any more Rings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.91,0:26:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他根本不知道我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the truth is he does not even know I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.20,0:26:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我在自己的地盘上做什么 跟他有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well. What business is it of his, how I conduct myself in my own realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.37,0:26:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,–凯勒布林博... –我不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Celebrimbor-- - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.58,0:26:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,无数生命危在旦夕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Countless lives are at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.12,0:26:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没时间耗费唇舌 说服他谁值得帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have not the time to bandy words about, convincing him who is worthy of aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.37,0:26:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不过吉尔加拉德迟早会发现真相的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nevertheless, sooner or later, Gil-galad will discover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposing he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.54,0:26:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.75,0:27:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向至高王祝贺三戒的功效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am congratulating the High King on the efficacy of The Three
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.16,0:27:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他我将关闭熔炉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and telling him that I am closing up the forge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.54,0:27:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,答应他我将尽快前往林顿会合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With a promise to join him in Lindon as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.33,0:27:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对至高王说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would lie to your High King?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.00,0:27:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在争取时间完成我们的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would grant us the space to complete our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.58,0:27:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为此我耗费了悠长岁月做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have spent an age preparing for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.04,0:27:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,成为学徒 潜心钻研\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have apprenticed, I have studied,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.70,0:27:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的技艺已达颠峰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have reached the very height of my craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.58,0:27:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是属于我的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This... This is my moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.04,0:27:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他别想夺走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, he will not take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉...真的很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, sorry, sorry! I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.33,0:30:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你是半兽人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you were an Orc!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.29,0:30:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 不太痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right. Doesn't hurt. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.87,0:30:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不太痛 痛死了吧 我刺伤你的大腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't hurt? Of course it hurts, I just stabbed you in the thigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.95,0:30:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还好啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could've been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.83,0:30:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,–来 我拔出来 –不要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here, let me pull it out. - No, don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.54,0:31:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,–不要拔出来比较好  –是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're meant to leave it in! - Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.16,0:31:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对 不管刺到哪 留着比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes! Whenever you're stabbed, you leave it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.16,0:31:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,–我没被刺过  –我也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never been stabbed before! Neither have I!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.29,0:31:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定不痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure it doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.66,0:31:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这下真痛死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, now it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.20,0:31:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.33,0:31:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.62,0:31:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我来就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, stop. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.08,0:31:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.91,0:31:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是艾丝翠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Estrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.41,0:31:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.87,0:31:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是臭海人 你是要往山脊线去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're Sea-folk. Were you headed for the ridgeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.91,0:31:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存者会在扎营处等我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The survivors will be waiting for us where we made camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.29,0:31:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.75,0:31:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能错过他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you may have missed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.54,0:32:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.66,0:32:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你去过了 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've already been there, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在找人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was searchin' for someone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.12,0:32:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那里只剩马蹄印和烂泥巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin' left but hoofprints and mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.70,0:32:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢 我发现这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But... I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.25,0:32:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 标记了一条路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. And there's a path marked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.33,0:32:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“佩拉基尔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Pelargir."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.50,0:32:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 父亲没有离开 他带大家去了那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. Father didn't leave, he led everyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,运气好的话 你朋友也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your folk too, any luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.87,0:33:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,佩拉基尔 努门诺尔旧聚落
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.91,0:33:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,港口没看到半艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't see any ships in the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.37,0:33:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,保持希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.45,0:33:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道会在那里找到谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no telling who we'll find down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.54,0:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你也在找家人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hoping to find kin as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.58,0:33:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我未婚夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.87,0:33:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.50,0:33:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,–怎么回事  –半兽人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's happened? - Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.08,0:34:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去佩拉基尔 被他们拦截\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was on me way to Pelargir when they waylaid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.95,0:34:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,–夺走了一切 –你还能行动吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Took everything. - Can you travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.04,0:34:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.79,0:34:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该继续前进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ought to keep movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.79,0:34:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,至少给他一点吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Least we can do is give him something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.00,0:34:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丝翠 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estrid, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.16,0:34:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抓好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grab hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.41,0:34:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berek!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.75,0:34:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该听那女孩的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should've listened to the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.16,0:35:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 上马 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go! Get the horse. Get on. Go! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.83,0:35:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 压低身子 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move. Get down. Come on. Let's go. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.33,0:35:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.00,0:35:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伊熙尔杜 还记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Isildur. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.16,0:35:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵的记忆不会黯淡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elven memories do not dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.79,0:36:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这片森林里 野人的数量是我们的好几倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wildmen outnumber us many to one in these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的马 我不能抛下它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My horse. I can't abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.70,0:36:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么做就怎么做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Settle your own affairs as seems you best.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.87,0:36:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我有我的事要忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have my own to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.83,0:36:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在佩拉基尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Pelargir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.08,0:36:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.29,0:38:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,纳维 跟国王报告...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi, Narvi! Tell the King about the weans.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.58,0:39:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽力了 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're doin' what we can. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.00,0:39:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽全力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we'll do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.04,0:39:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.79,0:39:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,纳维 国王知道孩子们饿肚子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi, does the King know the children are hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.70,0:39:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有点耐性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.79,0:39:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,纳维 拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 纳维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speak the truth, Narvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.62,0:39:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就去跟国王报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm speaking with the King now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.70,0:39:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我们跟国王说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speak to the King on our behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,纳维\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Narvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.58,0:39:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 粮商们在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sire. The food-merchants are outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.04,0:39:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来向您请愿打开国家粮仓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, they're going to petition you to open the royal grain-reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.16,0:39:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,粮食储备能撑多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long will the reserves last?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多数看法为...三个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By most accounts... Three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.08,0:39:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.20,0:39:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.00,0:40:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,凯勒布林博声称这些戒指 能带给我们解决困境的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor claims these Rings will give us the power to solve our dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.66,0:40:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,身为矮人 我有责任告知你他的提议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt it my duty as a Dwarf to bring you his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.33,0:40:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你要说的就是这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that all you come to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.54,0:40:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.04,0:41:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.25,0:41:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I am your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.95,0:41:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你一样坚毅 一样顽固\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm hard as you, stubborn as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.58,0:41:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一样一身傲气 还有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As crusted with pride. And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.66,0:41:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.87,0:41:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该不尊重你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wrong to disrespect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.08,0:41:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.16,0:41:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.83,0:41:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.00,0:41:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,矿工的拳头长满了老茧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miners have calloused fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.16,0:41:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,揍人很痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their punches land hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.16,0:41:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等你小孩长大再来说痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait till your children grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.95,0:42:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,父王...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.95,0:42:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,埃瑞吉安那种力量 我无法信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this power in Eregion, I don't trust it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.70,0:42:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me once,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.04,0:42:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵的命运是由 比我们更有智慧的存在决定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the fate of Elves is decided by wiser minds than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.41,0:42:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,试图扭转 试图逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That to try and alter it, to try and cheat death,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.58,0:42:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会导致更大的灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might lead to an even greater catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.04,0:42:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.54,0:42:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,万一你是对的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if you were right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.83,0:42:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你妈妈教你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did your mother teach you how to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.75,0:42:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.25,0:42:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What d'you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.62,0:43:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我失败了 我没能阻止阿达尔 没能...保护她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I failed. Failed to stop Adar. Failed... to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.83,0:43:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为她会好起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought she was getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.62,0:43:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的肉体无法承受 半兽人邪箭腥臭的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a foulness in Orc arrows not easily forgotten by human flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.79,0:43:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真好 伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pleases me to see you, Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.25,0:43:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,经历那场火山爆发的人 很少能撑到现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So few who slept in the fire made it this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.66,0:43:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,除了那些打上阿达尔印记的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}save those who took the Mark of Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.58,0:43:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望能和你父亲分享这份喜悦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I could share my relief with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.16,0:43:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有抛下你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He did not abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.75,0:43:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,努门诺尔会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Númenor will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.62,0:43:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你和家人会再次团聚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your family will be whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.08,0:44:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好有你在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These people are fortunate you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.00,0:44:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这村子需要治疗师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This village needs a healer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.45,0:44:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的治疗师刚刚火葬了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their healer just burned on a pyre.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.16,0:44:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你对贝烈瑞安德了解多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you know of Beleriand?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.25,0:44:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,精灵城 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf-city, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.12,0:44:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一整个精灵王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An entire Elf-realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那里出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was born there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.25,0:44:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如今它沉睡海底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, it lies under the wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.58,0:44:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,贝烈瑞安德被毁后 我充满愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After it fell, I felt such anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.00,0:44:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对魔苟斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Toward Morgoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.41,0:44:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但我最气的是我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I felt the most anger towards myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.95,0:45:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种永远无法平息的渴求 西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a thirst that can never be slaked, Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.75,0:45:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最终会带你走上毁灭之路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the end it will drink you dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.37,0:45:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 边走边弄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, yeah. More can do it in the same time, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.08,0:45:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你监视我们这么多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All those years you were watching us...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.45,0:45:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我父亲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}d'you ever know my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.50,0:45:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.41,0:45:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.08,0:45:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很清楚 你不是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I know this much, he wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.45,0:45:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间曾有的关联 现在也化为灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And anything you were to me, is ashes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.04,0:45:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是觉得 我们没必要再交谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So for my part, we don't ever need to speak again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.50,0:45:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦 我没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.75,0:45:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 再拿点木头来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fetch me some more of that wood, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.54,0:46:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对 那边那堆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, from that pile there. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.37,0:46:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是以前的努门诺尔留下的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is from old Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.83,0:46:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喷泉之类的 也不见喷半滴水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some fountain. Barely spits a drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.45,0:46:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是喷泉 是引水道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a fountain. It's an aqueduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.33,0:46:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,用来把水引到家中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's supposed to bring water into your homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.41,0:46:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,人类盖不出那种东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Men can't build things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.08,0:46:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在努门诺尔可以 你真该看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Númenor, we can. You should see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.58,0:46:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这么厉害 你干嘛离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it's so grand, why'd you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.08,0:46:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听说中洲有更厉害的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heard there were grander things in Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.08,0:46:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你真想找回你的马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}D'you really want your horse back?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.83,0:46:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道它在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.87,0:46:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚这里见 月升之时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meet me here. Tonight. Moonrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.75,0:47:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,带剑来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.54,0:47:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小心烧到自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't burn yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.04,0:47:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有你未婚夫的消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any word of your intended?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.79,0:47:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.45,0:47:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他会撑过来的 如果他有你一半坚强 我敢肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll make it. If he's even half as strong as you, I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.41,0:47:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没你想的那么坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not so strong as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.83,0:47:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很难不责怪自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard, not to blame myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.58,0:47:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,责怪自己什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.16,0:47:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.41,0:47:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,逃过一劫 太多人没能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For surviving. When so many others didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.00,0:48:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我十岁时失去了母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was ten when I lost my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.25,0:48:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我游离岸边太远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swam out further than I was supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.25,0:48:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,被大浪卷走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got caught in a riptide.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.75,0:48:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她淹死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.54,0:48:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为了救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.00,0:48:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在我妈...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After my mum--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.58,0:48:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想她现在过得怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep wondering what it's like for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.29,0:48:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我会在梦里看到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes, I see mine in dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.70,0:48:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像已经接受事实了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You seem to have found peace with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.87,0:49:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.12,0:49:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我刚跟你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, what I just told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.50,0:49:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家乡没人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}back home, nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.87,0:49:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只告诉大家她淹死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just told them she drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.41,0:49:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道是我害的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody knows it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.62,0:49:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从那时起我就觉得有义务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ever since, I've felt bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.91,0:49:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要做出与众不同的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To try and do something singular.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.50,0:49:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,特别的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.91,0:49:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要让她的牺牲值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To try and find a way to earn what she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.70,0:49:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道要怎么让牺牲值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if you can earn a thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.58,0:49:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是觉得你只要接受 当作一份礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you just have to accept it, as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.54,0:50:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你对她来说很珍贵 所以她自愿付出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One she gave freely because you were precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.50,0:50:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.66,0:51:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本没什么肉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.04,0:51:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 要省着点吃 森林里没什么东西可吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.75,0:51:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,–陷阱常常什么也没抓到 –情况越来越糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.25,0:51:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,–这根本吃不饱 –对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.79,0:51:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你也觉得冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.25,0:51:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,木材剩不多了 我知道我们需要...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.66,0:51:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,卡斯柏刚刚在说 我在想 如果我们选对了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.75,0:51:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托今晚别下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.33,0:51:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.41,0:51:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 我们一整天没吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.87,0:51:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望这次我们都生病
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.45,0:51:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天杀的冷得跟小刀儿剌似的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.58,0:51:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子 老鼠也有东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.91,0:51:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,–快好了 –让开 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.87,0:52:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.29,0:52:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我们偷来的马 我再去让它们安静下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just them trotters we stole. I'll quiet 'em down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.20,0:52:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,借一下火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Share your fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.95,0:52:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼 你那么晚在外面干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doin' out here in the dark, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.37,0:52:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到老妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lose your mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.12,0:52:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你们的伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm one o' you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.12,0:52:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我效忠阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I serve Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.25,0:52:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是阿达尔的印记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not Adar's brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.95,0:52:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这证明我为他做的比你们还多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's proof I've done more for him than any of you can claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.83,0:52:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.37,0:53:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看这家伙吃得白白胖胖 肯定来自佩拉基尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look how well-fed he is. I'll wager this one comes from Pelargir.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.41,0:53:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来袭击我们的吗  就像你们对付其他人那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you here to attack us, lad? Same as your folk done the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.20,0:53:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从未袭击你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've never attacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.50,0:53:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你们袭击我们三个营地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You attacked three of our camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.54,0:53:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.37,0:53:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.70,0:53:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有埋伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.37,0:53:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.50,0:53:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.70,0:53:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo! Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.75,0:55:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,撒谎女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen of lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.66,0:55:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她不配治国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's unfit to rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.54,0:55:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,典礼上除了国王或女王的祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No voice but the prayer of a king or a queen
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.08,0:55:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不允许有任何声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is permitted during this ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.83,0:55:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然而\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.62,0:55:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,努门诺尔的悲痛对我来说极为神圣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the grief of Númenor is sacred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.00,0:55:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的痛苦 就如同这国家的祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your pain, a prayer within these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.33,0:55:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到你们的悲伤 你们的愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear your sorrow, and your anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.29,0:55:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我感同身受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.70,0:55:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们浴血奋战 也被鲜血染红\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have bloodied and been bloodied.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.75,0:56:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但要知道 我们会找到自己的方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But know this... We will find our course.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.50,0:56:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们当中还有人想发言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should there be another among us who feels moved to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.83,0:56:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先问问自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}firstly ask yourself this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.50,0:56:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了谁而哭泣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for whom do you cry out?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.12,0:56:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我们已安葬之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For those we have already buried?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.70,0:56:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For your kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.66,0:56:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是为了你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.04,0:56:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为了伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.45,0:56:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在临终之前 国王对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With his dying words, the King spoke to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.95,0:57:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说一切就是从这个开始 她听取了建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and said it was from this... she took counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.62,0:57:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为这样 我们的亲人枉死中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is because of this, our kinsmen died in Middle-earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.16,0:57:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗精灵之石左右了你们的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This Elf-stone is your queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.79,0:57:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.33,0:57:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一派胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.79,0:57:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,努门诺尔真正的统治者 绝不会听信一介精灵神器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Númenor's true ruler would never place trust in an Elvish artifact.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.00,0:57:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去摧毁掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it away and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.00,0:57:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.79,0:57:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗帕蓝提尔是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The palantír is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.91,0:57:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.66,0:58:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,–精灵巫术  –杀人凶手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf sorcery! - Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.04,0:58:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,撒谎女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen of lies! Queen of lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.04,0:58:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,–黑魔法  –女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dark magic! To the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.54,0:58:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,–住手  –退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop! Stop! Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.12,0:58:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Míriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.62,0:58:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,–我的女王  –弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Queen! Míriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.62,0:58:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Save my Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.66,0:58:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Míriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.79,0:58:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.41,0:58:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Míriel! Míriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.45,0:59:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,法拉宗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.04,0:59:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大鹰选择了法拉宗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The eagle favors Pharaz?n!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.54,1:00:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,法拉宗...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n! Pharaz?n!

